    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for daily transportation. The engine and transmission are in good working order, ensuring dependable performance on the road. However, please note that the exterior shows some visible wear, including minor scratches and faded paint in a few spots. The interior is clean but exhibits signs of age, such as some wear on the upholstery. It is a solid, functional car that would benefit from some minor cosmetic attention.",
      "price": 19500.0,
